---
title: Smothered Chicken with Onion Gravy plus Mashed Potatoes & Garlicky Green Beans
description: Got yourself a new boo and you’re ready to make it “Kitchen Official?” This is one of those feels-like-home recipes that’s absolutely guaranteed to please. You’ll season a pair of chicken cutlets with garlic and rosemary, seared to perfection in a hot pan, then drape them in a rich, velvety onion gravy. On the side are buttery sour cream mashed potatoes with even more of that luscious, savory gravy, and garlicky roasted green beans. After this meal, the rest of the evening should be …well, gravy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HFUSRC_R15724A_Hero_SmotheredChickenWithOnionGravy_W48_17_2025_Web-e75af8df.jpg
